	<h1>Welcome to The Story Swap</h1>
			
	<p>The Story Swap is an online community where people can be authentic and real, exchanging personal stories through video, and engaging in discussion around shared experiences. </p>

	<p>Join us in celebrating the launch of The Story Swap! Submit your story and enter to win one of three a $100 Amazon Gift Card prizes!</p>

	<h2>Contest</h2>
	<p> Submit a story of 5-15 minutes in length about what makes you who you are today. </p>

	<p>We are seeking thoughtful, reflective, and detailed submissions that go deeper than an everyday conversation. Let us know the real you!</p>

	<p>Don’t have a story to tell, but still want to be in the contest? Refer a friend to submit their
 story, and if they win, you will get your own $50 Amazon Gift Card!</p>

	<p>Stories will be rated on the following three categories, based on upvotes, so make sure to share your story with friends and family! <p>

	<ul>
