		<li>Most...</li>
		<li>Most...</li>
	</ul>

	<p>Keep in mind two guidelines to abide by</p>

	<ol>
		<li>Be authentic and real</li>
		<li>Keep the story about you</li>

	</ol>

	<p><strong>Deadline to submit is May XX</strong>. You can record yourself on your phone or computer, you can have a friend record you, or you can record yourself speaking at an event. The quality and art of your storytelling is less important than the raw emotion and meaning behind the story you tell. 
	</p>

	<p>We can’t wait to hear your stories! </p>
   
   <a href="/submit" class="btn btn-default"><span class="fa fa-user"></span>Submit your story</a>
		
